	"system": {
		"description": "<p>Your bonded artifact will not easily permit you to slip from their grasp. Whenever you would drop to 0 hit points, you instead gain 1 hit point and your bonded artifact gains control of you. You are compelled to take certain actions during the next minute, to the best of your ability, determined by the narrator. </p><p>If you drop to 0 hit points again while in this state, you fall unconscious and make death saving throws as normal. Once your bonded artifact gains control in this way, it cannot do so again until you finish a long rest. </p>",
